398
00:36:19,408 --> 00:36:21,245
[MICHAEL] Look, right there.

399
00:37:04,232 --> 00:37:08,495
[ADAM] Golf re-capitulates evolution.

400
00:37:08,931 --> 00:37:12,846
'Tis a microcosm of the world...

401
00:37:13,172 --> 00:37:17,280
a projection of all of our hopes and fears.

402
00:37:17,627 --> 00:37:21,435
Take our love of the balls flight...

403
00:37:21,628 --> 00:37:25,059
the sight of it hanging there in space...

404
00:37:25,437 --> 00:37:29,435
anticipates our desire for transcendence.

405
00:37:29,560 --> 00:37:37,214
The thrill of seeing it fly over the land, over
obstacles, especially over a stretch of water...

406
00:37:37,258 --> 00:37:39,231
and then onto the green...

407
00:37:40,445 --> 00:37:42,007
and into the hole.

408
00:37:42,998 --> 00:37:47,421
Ahh...that's a mystical quality...

409
00:37:48,087 --> 00:37:51,556
There is something in us,
something in all of us...

410
00:37:52,196 --> 00:37:53,965
that loves that flight.

411
00:37:54,122 --> 00:37:56,920
[EVE] The flight of the alone to the alone.

412
00:37:57,862 --> 00:38:00,175
[SHIVAS] That's the sound we want.

