him with this kind of thinking.

440
00:41:00,139 --> 00:41:01,996
[ADAM] Have you ever thought about that?

441
00:41:02,123 --> 00:41:03,798
[LANGE] What was it?

442
00:41:04,313 --> 00:41:07,759
The flight of the alone to the alone?

443
00:41:09,914 --> 00:41:15,977
[LANGE] I mean, seriously, are you equating your average
