444
00:41:16,038 --> 00:41:18,537
[ADAM] It's so, so real.

445
00:41:18,693 --> 00:41:21,455
[EVE] We know in our souls
what we are meant to be...

446
00:41:22,028 --> 00:41:26,450
so we are attracted by any
glimpse of greater possibilities.

447
00:41:27,065 --> 00:41:30,330
