marvelous state of mind...

449
00:41:33,929 --> 00:41:40,553
where the conflict of matter
and mind, body and spirit...

450
00:41:40,834 --> 00:41:41,922
are resolved.

451
00:41:48,564 --> 00:41:52,850
[SHIVAS] Sometimes you think the
ball will just never come down.

452
00:41:53,085 --> 00:41:53,969
[MICHAEL] Yes!

